info.name: CGY_QFL_CSS
info.additionalInfo:
- Only BTC pairs will show the styling.
- Colors coin pairs based off of MONTHLY volume!
- Now works for all exchanges.
- Squishes the pairs so they don't take so much space on the pair list and you can see more.

Update this style once or twice per month for latest pair colors. Because it's based on monthly volume, the pair colors don't change that often, but it's enough to see quickly which coins have the highest volume.

Montly Volume		
firebrick-------$0.00------------------to-$99,999,999.00
darkorange--$100,000,000.00----to-$199,999,999.00
gold-----------$200,000,000.00----to-$999,999,999.00
green---------$1,000,000,000.00--to-$1,999,999,999.00
aqua----------$2,000,000,000.00--to-$5,000,000,000,000.00


Feel free to send Ether if you find this useful :)
